{"word":"G691 - ἀργέω - argéō - arg-eh'-o - Linger","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀργέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">argéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">arg-eh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Linger</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - அயர்ந்திரு"},{"paragraph":"to be idle, inactive; contextually, to linger, delay"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G692 - ἀργός - argós - ar-gos'/692\">G692</a>; to <i>be idle</i>, that is, (figuratively) to <i>delay:</i> - linger.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2673/2673\">G2673</a>, <a href=\"#/G691/691\">G691</a>, <a href=\"#/G692/692\">G692</a>"}]}